org.efaps.admin.event

Enum EventType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EventType>
      • org.efaps.admin.event.EventType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<EventType>

    public enum EventType
extends Enum<EventType>
    This enumeration provides the key-value Relation for the TriggerEvent.
    Therefore using a trigger can be made by using the key. An example for the use of this enumeration is the definition of a Trigger inside the XML definition.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    The eFaps Team
